                    </div>
                    <span>This is a nice, inexpensive book to have in your collection or even to teach an introductory poetry class from.  It has a lot of good material, Poe, Dickinson, Frost, etc.  <p>And hey, it's a buck...why not?</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">best 80 cents I ever spent!</div>
